@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_odhivm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.99
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v0 + 0.08 - v1 + 0.11)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.14 * tmp + 0.48)) - ((v2 + 0.22 / v2 + 0.65) * v1))
    data[tid] = v0
